<h1>砭</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#990000;">biān</span><span class=alesi>(bian1)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 砭 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 砭</h2><div class=abo>
